PubMLST,is,a,site,that,hosts,publicly,accessible,Multilocus,Sequence,Typing,MLST,databases,and,software,It,provides,means,of,accessing,these,databases,in,common,formats,suitable,for,easy,linking,and,importation,to,local,resources,The,PubMLST,API,enables,software,developers,to,write,applications,that,can,query,the,MLST,databases,directly,without,using,the,standard,web,interface,It,uses,SOAP,protocol,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML